WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.700 --> 00:00:05.966
Greetings, Lady Wang.

2
00:00:09.733 --> 00:00:11.366
Hey, your face...

3
00:00:11.866 --> 00:00:15.166
Replying to Lady Wang, yesterday I unfortunately caught a cold.

4
00:00:15.166 --> 00:00:17.500
And this blush...

5
00:00:17.500 --> 00:00:18.400
I just applied it a bit heavily.

6
00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:19.633
With this look...

7
00:00:20.166 --> 00:00:20.700
How dare you...

8
00:00:20.700 --> 00:00:22.966
show yourself in front of His Majesty and the Empress Dowager?

9
00:00:22.966 --> 00:00:24.600
Yes, yes, please let me be eliminated quickly.

10
00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:26.800
I actually think this makeup is quite lovely.

11
00:00:32.133 --> 00:00:33.500
Greetings, Your Majesty.

12
00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:35.033
Empress Dowager.

13
00:00:39.366 --> 00:00:41.233
Raise your head.

14
00:00:45.766 --> 00:00:49.533
Emperor, what is good about this makeup?

15
00:00:49.533 --> 00:00:51.400
This makeup is festive.

16
00:00:53.166 --> 00:00:54.400
You may all rise.

17
00:00:59.533 --> 00:01:00.700
Today is the selection day.

18
00:01:00.900 --> 00:01:03.300
Yet her parents dressed her like this.

19
00:01:03.533 --> 00:01:06.466
It seems they usually mistreat her at home.

20
00:01:06.466 --> 00:01:08.200
Someone, convey my decree.

21
00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:09.933
Punish Minister Su by halving his salary for six months.

22
00:01:09.933 --> 00:01:12.233
And his wife will copy the "Classic of Women" a thousand times.

23
00:01:13.566 --> 00:01:15.900
In her past life, the empress's parents always caused trouble.

24
00:01:15.933 --> 00:01:18.866
I might as well take this opportunity to vent on the empress.

25
00:01:19.366 --> 00:01:21.266
What madness has this dog emperor come down with?

26
00:01:21.466 --> 00:01:23.200
In the past life, he didn't even show his face,

27
00:01:23.200 --> 00:01:24.800
letting the Empress Dowager decide everything.

28
00:01:24.800 --> 00:01:28.066
Emperor, your decree is too hasty.

29
00:01:28.266 --> 00:01:29.066
Hmph.

30
00:01:29.466 --> 00:01:31.033
Before I came, I looked at the roster.

31
00:01:31.133 --> 00:01:32.900
These two should be sisters.

32
00:01:32.900 --> 00:01:34.333
The younger sister is dressed in fine clothes,

33
00:01:34.333 --> 00:01:35.266
with exquisite makeup,

34
00:01:35.266 --> 00:01:37.366
while the elder sister looks like this.

35
00:01:37.700 --> 00:01:40.033
If this isn't favoritism, what is it?

36
00:01:41.666 --> 00:01:42.933
The emperor is right.

37
00:01:42.933 --> 00:01:46.000
To treat daughters so differently, indeed they should be punished.

38
00:01:46.366 --> 00:01:48.233
Take the Su girl away and redo her makeup.

39
00:01:48.566 --> 00:01:51.700
Please, go ahead.

40
00:01:59.600 --> 00:02:02.800
It's over. Now you're in trouble too.

41
00:02:02.800 --> 00:02:04.400
What on earth are you planning to do?

42
00:02:10.566 --> 00:02:13.300
Wow, is this the same person from earlier?

43
00:02:13.333 --> 00:02:14.600
So beautiful!

44
00:02:14.600 --> 00:02:16.800
She looks like a completely different person!

45
00:02:17.333 --> 00:02:18.900
Wow, such beauty!

46
00:02:19.266 --> 00:02:20.800
The emperor has a good eye.

47
00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:23.466
This Su girl is truly a rare beauty.

48
00:02:23.466 --> 00:02:26.500
Of course, Su Taifu is a famous great scholar.

49
00:02:26.766 --> 00:02:29.666
How could his granddaughter be anything less?

50
00:02:29.733 --> 00:02:32.000
This dog emperor really knows how to stir things up.

51
00:02:32.400 --> 00:02:33.500
Grandfather, I'm sorry.

52
00:02:33.500 --> 00:02:35.700
Your granddaughter might embarrass you next.